      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation software (Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2) used under a documented quality management system with version control, regression testing, and audit trail. Required level 2 for model risk 3 with medium decision consequence.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 was operated under an FDA 21 CFR Part 11-compliant QMS. Version control records, regression test suite results, and change-control logs were reviewed. Achieved level 3 exceeds the required level 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
